title: Personal Stats
text:
Sample Plot
Here’s a simple plot using built-in R data:

ggplot(mtcars, aes(x = wt, y = mpg, color = factor(cyl))) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(title = "Car Weight vs. MPG",
       x = "Weight (1000 lbs)",
       y = "Miles per Gallon",
       color = "Cylinders") +
  theme_minimal()
